title: War of the Roses: The Panty Drawer Was Rooted Through
description: Tessa's boyfriend Eli was dog-sitting while she was out of town recently and when she got back her roommate said that Eli had gone through her panty drawer AND something was missing that is leading Tessa to wonder if Eli is cheating.  We find out on War of the Roses!
